{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迎击战～晚夏使者愁纷纷～ 你与我相同",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "库菈乌之所以会关心拉托妮，\\n是因为她也有选择孤独、忍受寂寞的过往。\\n得到库菈乌肯定的拉托妮敞开心扉，\\n下定决心要和库菈乌\\n一起解决这次的事件。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我是个坏孩子，\\n是会给大家带来痛苦的\\n邪恶的奈亚拉托提普。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "所以我要一个人，去一个\\n不为人知的地方。因为我已经……\\n不想再给别人添麻烦了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "拉托妮，你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "没关系的……别管我。\\n感谢你至今为止的照顾……\\n别了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不要，我不会让你走的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "诶？库、库菈乌？\\n为什么……不行，放开我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我不放。你的表情那么痛苦，\\n我不能就这么丢下你\\n一个人不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "一开始我不就说了嘛。\\n我想看到你的笑容，\\n才自作主张做这些的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我不懂……我真的不懂。\\n为什么你要这么关心我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "因为你——\\n和以前的我一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "一样？和你吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是的。我们都曾觉得是自己的错，\\n试图把自己封闭起来……\\n你那副模样和我太像了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以我不能丢下你不管。\\n拉托妮，你愿意听我说吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我以前——其实害死过人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "很久以前——我不顾父母的反对，\\n离开故乡，在千里之外的圣城工作。\\n当时的圣城正是战争的最前线。\\n父母不知给我寄过多少封信\\n催促我回家。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "可是我……因为些许逆反心理，\\n我总是在给父母的回信里\\n写一些安抚的话。\\n而这最终导致了父母的死。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "父母为了带我回家乡避难\\n而离开了森林，在途中丧命……\\n这相当于是我害死了他们。\\n我对自己感到绝望，自那以后\\n一直躲在自己的房间不出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "我觉得自己已经\\n没资格与他人接触了。\\n\\n但是……\\n那个人没有丢下我不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "你好啊，库菈乌。\\n我给你送饭来了。\\n能顺便和你聊聊吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "穆穆雅娜……\\n我之前也已经说过了，\\n不要和我扯上关系。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "如果你是真心不想与他人接触，\\n我会尊重你的决定。\\n但是……并不是这样吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "你看，你的脸上写满了孤独。\\n所以我想陪在你的身边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不行……我会给你带来麻烦的。\\n害死了父母的我，\\n没有资格让人陪在我身边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以让我独处就好。\\n我就该孤身一人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "库菈乌，才不是这样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "和他人在一起并不需要资格。\\n而且我是自愿来你这里的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "不管你做了什么……\\n我都不会觉得你是麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "就算你这么说……\\n现在的我也无法接受。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "是吗？你不接受也无所谓。\\n只是我想陪着你，所以我会\\n一直像这样握着你的手。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "直到你找回重新振作的力量，\\n我都决不会丢下你\\n一个人不管的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110386_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆雅娜",
            "context": "这就是我的心愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那个人对我来说是一位\\n“好姐姐”。就算我对她冷淡，\\n她也不离不弃地一直陪着我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "每当我用“我一个人就好”\\n“我就该孤身一人”这种话拒绝她，\\n她都会予以否定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "“一个人”……就好？啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_02",
                "120144_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我一个人待着就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "没关系的……\\n我就该一个人独处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "和我……一样。\\n库菈乌以前……\\n也说过……这种话吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是的。因为我也和你一样……\\n曾经擅长一味抑制自己，\\n却又害怕孤独。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "不过，我那颗孤独的心……\\n不知何时被她的温柔所拯救。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以如果你和当年的我一样，\\n因为厌恶自己\\n而感到孤独……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我想陪在你身边，\\n直到你不再这么想，\\n就像当初那个人对我一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我会陪你直到你不再伪装\\n自己的内心，不再说出\\n一个人就好的这种话！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我懂了……\\n原来是这样。库菈乌……\\n我现在，终于明白了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我……一直以来都在自欺欺人。\\n说什么一个人就好是假话，\\n说自己就该独处也是假话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我要留下来看家，不能去\\n逛祭典的时候，其实很孤独。\\n说要独自回圣城的时候也很孤独。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "我不想孤零零一个人！\\n我其实……不想孤身一人，\\n想和其他人待在一起。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你一直都忍受着\\n这种孤独的心情呢。\\n没事的，你不用再孤独了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "库菈乌……谢谢你。\\n不过，有些不可思议……\\n库菈乌以前竟然和我一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你反感吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "不……我反而安心了。\\n现在……我应该……是开心的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "有相同心境的人陪着我……\\n我就不再孤单了。\\n我一定能坚持下去。所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "这次我想和你一起\\n解决这个事件。\\n我可以……这么希望吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯，当然了！\\n让我们齐心协力\\n解决这次事件吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊、哈啊……\\n怎么会……到处都找不到\\n奈亚拉托提普！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "嗯、嗯……究竟，去了哪里！？\\n不快点找到的话，\\n事态会一发不可收拾！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "往西南方向的小镇前进——\\n奈亚拉托提普就在那里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "你是那个……\\n为我们开门的亡灵！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "亡灵……竟然真的存在吗。\\n你到底是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亡灵",
            "context": "我是……因妻子举行的\\n异端仪式而被唤来的魂魄。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110349_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "拉托妮",
            "context": "妻子？啊，你难道是……\\n死去的班戈？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120040_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亡灵",
            "context": "是的。为了阻止妻子的行为，\\n我一直以这副样子拼命反抗，\\n希望有人能救救我妻子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22215_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_20"
            ],
